Title: Baryonium annihilation into meson+vector meson

Abstract: Assuming that the decay of baryonium into meson+vector meson proceeds through an intermediate virtual vector meson, some selection rules and branching ratios of this decay are derived from the octet version of unitary symmetry.

Keywords: Particle physics, Physics, Political science, Nuclear physics, Law
